<paragraph blockId="13.[95,1229,696,1136]" pageId="13" pageNumber="354">
<keyLead pageId="13" pageNumber="354">2. Metatarsi white or creamy-white in colour. Apex of antenna reach middle of urosternite III. Translucent panels of elytra reach base of elytra..........................................................................................................3</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[95,1229,696,1136]" pageId="13" pageNumber="354">
<keyLead pageId="13" pageNumber="354">
— Metatarsi dark chestnut in colour. Apex of antenna reach apex of urosternite III. Translucent panels of elytra do not reach base of elytra. 
<collectingCountry box="[434,493,920,944]" name="Brazil" pageId="13" pageNumber="354">Brazil</collectingCountry>
